Package gameData

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Activity
    The Activity class stores the data of activity
    Controller
    The Head class of entire project witch provides cooperation between algorithmic and GUI parts except mini-games
    Course
    Stores the data of course
    DataBase
    DataBase class that gives static access to important game data.
    Day
    The Day class stores the data of day
    Distribution
    The Distribution is an abstract class that stores the data of activity's distribution, each Activity has it's own Distribution which is representing activity's effects on player's statistics at depend on time influence (rounds)
    ExponentialDistribution
    The ExponentialDistribution class is extending of Distribution class, and stores the data of distribution
    GameCalendar
    The GameCalendar class stores the semesters
    Item
    This class consists all parameters, which represents item and consists public method that operate on items or return item's parameter
    Lecturer
    The Lecturer class stores the data of lecturer
    Log
    This class represents the log that deposits a game's history.It also contains method that operates on log
    NormalDistribution
    The NormalDistribution class is extending of Distribution class, and stores the data of distribution
    Player
    The Player class stores the data of player and methods that operate on player's parameters
    RandomEvent
    The RandomEvent class stores the data of event
    Semester
    The Semester class stores the days
    Shop
    Class represents shop, which is an ArrayList of Item and contains methods
    UniformDistribution
    The UniformDistribution class is extending of Distribution class, and stores the data of distribution
    XMLhandler
    XMLhandler handles loading and saving game information from files.
